  "tells": [
    "Know when to switch between aggro and control modes based on the board state",
    "Flash in Spirits at instant speed to maximize combat tricks and utility",
    "Prioritize tapping down opponent's key creatures before they can attack or block",
    "Common mistakes include overcommitting to the board without interaction, mismanaging mana for instant-speed triggers, forgetting to use Cryptbreaker\u2019s ability, and not tracking the opponent\u2019s graveyard for No More Lies.",
    "Unique interactions: Rattlechains can shut down key blockers mid-combat."
